title: Coke and hookers - go big or go home
text: 14:53 creampuff said: According to the article it was only herbal viagara. I wonder what the dosage equivalence is with normal viagara? Could be anything. Some so-called "natural" treatments are anything but, and contain mixtures of prescription drugs as well as a cocktail of other ingredients.Some of the "herbal" alternatives to Viagra have been found to cause genuinely dangerous fluctuations in blood pressure - which could be the cause of the problem on this case.Almost certainly won't be the 'nearly a bottle' of brandy over four days, unless it was super-strength or actually a four-gallon bottle.
